wikipedia_page.main: James "Dobby" Dobb (born 1972 in Derby) is an English former professional motocross racer. Amongst his achievements, he was crowned amca 125 world champion  Motocross World Champion in 2001, and was a top rider in the AMA motocross and supercross series during the mid-1990s.
